Arnold 4.2 Renderer Info Plug-in
================================

Environment Variables
---------------------

KATANA_HOME  The Katana installation directory at compile-time

Building
--------

1. Ensure the environment variables listed above have been set.
2. Run 'make'.
3. Copy 'out/ArnoldRendererInfo.so' to the 'Libs' subdirectory within
   a Katana resources path.
